    "en": {
      "title": "Post Office 3 days a week",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "In view of the crisis situation in the country, all post offices will be open only three days a week until the 10th of next month or until further notice, Post Master General Ranjith Ariyaratne said in a circular.",
        "According to the circular, all post offices will be open on Tuesdays, Wednesdays and Thursdays and post offices will be closed on Mondays, Fridays and Saturdays."
      ],
